1
00:00:36,719 --> 00:00:38,200
Mengna Valley fell and we survived

2
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:39,240
We'll be fine this time too

3
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:40,399
Let's go. We'll figure it out outside

4
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:41,560
Wait

5
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:51,079
Come on, stop dragging your feet

6
00:00:51,079 --> 00:00:52,039
Move it, before this place collapses

7
00:00:52,039 --> 00:00:52,759
Let's go!

8
00:01:14,359 --> 00:01:15,920
Shu Tong, are you okay?

9
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:19,959
Chen Youxi, that ceremony at Mengna Valley

10
00:01:20,799 --> 00:01:22,280
didn't it get interrupted halfway through

11
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,959
when people started vomiting and fainting?

12
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:27,280
Even going mad and killing each other?

13
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:30,079
Yeah, why?

14
00:01:31,879 --> 00:01:33,040
I just noticed something

15
00:01:33,719 --> 00:01:35,200
On the walls inside this cave

16
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:38,359
there are wave-like ring patterns

17
00:01:38,439 --> 00:01:39,760
What? What?

18
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:40,359
What patterns?

19
00:01:40,359 --> 00:01:42,840
Legend tells of a small city

20
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:45,840
filled with many guardian statues

21
00:01:46,439 --> 00:01:47,519
And inside those statues

22
00:01:47,959 --> 00:01:49,760
were these very same ring patterns

23
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:51,400
They were placed by the sea

24
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,760
to prevent underwater enemy attacks

25
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:55,200
How did they defend?

26
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:56,799
With infrasound

27
00:01:57,799 --> 00:02:00,439
The statues were placed by the sea

28
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,640
so they had water inside them

29
00:02:03,159 --> 00:02:04,719
Once someone touched the statue

30
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:06,519
or the water rippled abnormally

31
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:07,840
the water inside

32
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,719
would react with the wave patterns

33
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,039
inside the statue

34
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,199
producing a kind of sound wave

35
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:16,400
A sound wave below 20 Hertz

36
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:19,400
The sound waves our ears normally detect

37
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:22,039
fall within 20 to 20,000 Hertz

38
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,240
Though we can't sense infrasound

39
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:26,439
once it passes through our bodies

40
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:28,560
it can trigger emotional disturbances

41
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,840
or even hallucinations

42
00:02:31,039 --> 00:02:32,919
severely damaging our nervous system

43
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:35,039
What does any of this have to do with us?

44
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,560
Advisor He means

45
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,479
the disaster that struck Mengna Valley

46
00:02:39,159 --> 00:02:41,400
and the cave collapse just now

47
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:44,199
might be linked to infrasound

48
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:45,639
But there's no water in the cave

49
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,840
How could there be resonance?

50
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:49,639
The tremor in the cave just now

51
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:52,719
from the arrow grazing the Lingxiao Pearl

52
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,000
I'm thinking

53
00:02:54,639 --> 00:02:56,199
the Lingxiao Pearl's vibration

54
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:58,080
must have shaken the pool water

55
00:02:58,639 --> 00:02:59,919
If my guess is right

56
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,000
the walls of this pool

57
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:03,439
must also have wave patterns on them

58
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:05,159
So

59
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,479
the infrasound generated in the pool

60
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:10,599
resonated with the entire cave

61
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:13,400
Which means the infrasound

62
00:03:13,599 --> 00:03:16,159
got amplified countless times in the cave

63
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:18,639
That's why it created such immense energy

64
00:03:20,879 --> 00:03:22,039
In my dream

65
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,039
the disaster that befell Mengna Valley

66
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,759
started with the pool shaking

67
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:28,319
Now the biggest problem is

68
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:31,360
if the real culprit behind all this

69
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,599
is truly infrasound

70
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:38,159
then no matter how we run

71
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,879
we can't escape it

72
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,400
Why?

73
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,800
Infrasound has a very low frequency

74
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:50,599
The atmosphere barely absorbs it

75
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,280
It is highly penetrating

76
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:54,159
and travels great distances

77
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:56,639
Infrasound from quakes and nuclear blasts

78
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,400
can destroy buildings outright

79
00:03:58,479 --> 00:04:01,280
Once it resonates with nearby objects

80
00:04:01,319 --> 00:04:03,000
it generates even more massive energy

81
00:04:03,319 --> 00:04:04,400
The most lethal part is

82
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,879
the vibration frequencies of many organs

83
00:04:07,599 --> 00:04:09,319
are very close to infrasound

84
00:04:11,039 --> 00:04:12,639
Once the two align

85
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:16,000
it triggers resonance in our organs

86
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:19,839
which can cause fatal organ damage

87
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:22,040
No wonder I feel so awful

88
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:25,079
So that was it, infrasound's behind this?

89
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:29,000
Listen, let's just push through

90
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,000
and keep moving for now

91
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,480
Okay

92
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,240
Go

93
00:04:41,519 --> 00:04:42,160
Go

94
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,319
Go

95
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:44,279
Old Lu

96
00:04:46,519 --> 00:04:49,279
Mengna Valley fell because of infrasound

97
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:52,240
The pool's vibration produced the infrasound

98
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:21,079
Chen Youxi

99
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,639
Wait for me.

100
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:43,040
Chen Youxi!

101
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:47,600
Chen Youxi!

102
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:53,240
Chen Youxi, what're you doing? Chen Youxi!

103
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:41,279
Chen Youxi, get out here!

104
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:54,160
Advisor He! Chen Youxi!

105
00:07:55,399 --> 00:07:56,240
Advisor He!

106
00:07:57,879 --> 00:07:59,720
Hurry, let's go, Advisor He!

107
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:02,199
I have to go save Chen Youxi!

108
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:03,519
Move!

109
00:08:04,879 --> 00:08:06,680
Hurry!

110
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:34,919
Chen Youxi is still in there!

111
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:36,120
Chen Youxi!

112
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:36,840
Advisor He!

113
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:38,039
Chen Youxi!

114
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:39,120
You can't go, Advisor He!

115
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,000
Let go of me, please!

116
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,399
He'll die in there!

117
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,600
Let me go in!

118
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,720
Chen Youxi! Advisor He!

119
00:09:44,799 --> 00:09:45,320
What are you doing?

120
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:48,000
Even if I die, I'll die with him!

121
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,600
Let me in, Sister Shu Tong!

122
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,039
I'm begging you!

123
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:51,440
No!

124
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:54,600
Please, let go of me, let go!

125
00:09:57,840 --> 00:10:00,440
Chen Youxi, get out here!

126
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,600
Chen Youxi!

127
00:10:13,879 --> 00:10:14,679
Advisor He.

128
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,320
Trust me.

129
00:10:17,399 --> 00:10:18,399
I have a gut feeling.

130
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:20,200
Old Chen has nine lives.

131
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:22,080
He'll definitely come out safe and sound.

132
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,600
Brother Chen is going to be fine.

133
00:10:24,679 --> 00:10:27,039
The only thing we can do now

134
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:28,799
is wait quietly.

135
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:30,600
Fatty, come here.

136
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,399
Give me your hand.

137
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,039
Close your eyes.

138
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,279
Pray.

139
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:50,879
Just wait.

140
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,480
He'll come out safely, I know it.

141
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:09,919
What's up?

142
00:12:09,679 --> 00:12:10,639
Everyone, pack up.

143
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:13,159
We can follow this river out of here.

144
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:17,080
Where should I toss it?

145
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,000
Here goes!

146
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:39,559
So peaceful

147
00:12:39,559 --> 00:12:40,000
Alright

148
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,440
Okay, come on

149
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,200
Come, drink up, drink up

150
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,600
Try Old Chen's brew, come on

151
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,039
Cheers

152
00:12:44,559 --> 00:12:46,279
"Your" Old Chen, what a way to put it

153
00:12:47,759 --> 00:12:48,240
Old Lu

154
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:51,000
I can't bear to part with you either

155
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:53,360
Why don't you think it over

156
00:12:54,039 --> 00:12:56,559
Come abroad with us, why not?

157
00:12:56,679 --> 00:12:58,960
Big Fatty, we've been buddies

158
00:12:59,559 --> 00:13:00,879
Hearing that is enough

159
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:02,399
Lao Zhu

160
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,360
Back in the early years

161
00:13:05,159 --> 00:13:05,799
because of the wars

162
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:07,519
so many of our country's cultural relics

163
00:13:07,759 --> 00:13:09,159
were all lost abroad

164
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,960
When we head out this time

165
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:13,399
we'll definitely keep an eye out for you

166
00:13:13,799 --> 00:13:16,840
Whenever we find treasures lost abroad

167
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:18,039
we'll bring them back to you

168
00:13:18,399 --> 00:13:19,159
Good

169
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,679
Since you've already decided

170
00:13:21,679 --> 00:13:23,279
to go abroad with Advisor He

171
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,879
just settle down

172
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,320
and do what you need to do

173
00:13:27,679 --> 00:13:29,919
I won't say much more

174
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:32,720
You've all worked hard all this time

175
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:35,639
Take good care of yourselves from now on

176
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,480
Honestly

177
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:41,480
I can't bear to part with the Advance team

178
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:46,360
And I hope you won't forget me, Lao Zhu

179
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:49,720
Let's all take care of ourselves from now on

180
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,320
Alright

181
00:13:50,559 --> 00:13:51,000
Come on

182
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:52,720
Come on

183
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,399
Take care of yourselves

184
00:13:56,039 --> 00:13:56,840
Cheers

185
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:59,320
So you mean

186
00:13:59,919 --> 00:14:01,440
this infrasound

187
00:14:01,799 --> 00:14:04,720
can reveal the images we desire most

188
00:14:05,559 --> 00:14:06,600
So I'm thinking

189
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,879
the Queen of Meng Na Gu

190
00:14:07,879 --> 00:14:10,440
during the Imperial Sacrifice Ceremony

191
00:14:10,519 --> 00:14:12,600
saw Mengna Valley under her rule

192
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:13,519
expanding its territory

193
00:14:13,519 --> 00:14:14,519
passed down for generations

194
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:17,399
But that may have just been her mind

195
00:14:17,399 --> 00:14:18,840
stimulated by the infrasound

196
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,480
producing a kind of hallucination

197
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:23,240
showing her what she most wanted to see

198
00:14:23,799 --> 00:14:25,200
It was just her desire

199
00:14:25,399 --> 00:14:26,720
not something that actually existed

200
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:29,240
Then when you returned to the altar

201
00:14:29,519 --> 00:14:31,000
what hallucination did you see?

202
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,080
What?

203
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,120
You know, these foreigners

204
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:28,200
I love you, I love you, I love you

205
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:29,519
say it several times a day

206
00:15:29,919 --> 00:15:32,240
For us Chinese, saying "I love you" once

207
00:15:32,759 --> 00:15:34,000
isn't easy at all

208
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:35,720
What's the big deal?

209
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:38,320
"I love you" isn't just for lovers

210
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:40,200
Parents and children can say it too

211
00:15:40,799 --> 00:15:46,200
I love you, I love you, I love you

212
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,840
If you love someone, you should say it

213
00:15:48,519 --> 00:15:50,120
From now on, when you're with me

214
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,840
you have to say it to me ten times a day

215
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:53,399
Okay

216
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:54,840
You promised me

217
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,200
I promised you

218
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:14,799
I love you

219
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,320
You said it had to be ten times

220
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:27,679
I love you, I love you, I love you

221
00:16:29,879 --> 00:16:30,679
I love you
